[SN]TITLE[SN]
Cash calendar - financial tips for February

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Valentine's Day dominates the month of February for many retailers, but how can consumers keep the costs under control?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
1 February 2016 Last updated at 00:18 GMT
The BBC News website asked the independent Money Advice Service to deliver a calendar of month-by-month tips for those trying to keep their personal finances in order.
Andy Webb, from the service, says that the key for lovebirds in February is to shop around.
